             were indicted for <rs id="t18220911-150-off789" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220911-150-off789" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-150-off789" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220911-150-cd790" type="crimeDate">9th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-150-off789 t18220911-150-cd790"></join>, two bushels of chaff, value 16 d.; one bushel of bran, value 10 d.; two pecks of beans, value 2 s.; and two bags, value 3 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220911-150-victim1421" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Lambert
                  <interp inst="t18220911-150-victim1421" type="surname" value="Lambert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-150-victim1421" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-150-victim1421" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
